dc_title_s: Hydro (Polygon and Line) Taylor County, WI 2015
dc_description_s: This data layer represents hydrography for Taylor County, Wisconsin in 2015. It is a feature class within the geodatabase “Taylor_Hydro_2015.gdb”. The feature layers included in this geodatabase are “Taylor_HydroLine_2015” and “Taylor_HydroPoly_2015'. [HydroPoly: Water features such as Lakes, Reservoirs, Wide Streams and River, and Unspecified Open Water features.]
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements.
